title: Leah Freeman // 82
description:
In the summer of 2000, a 15-year-old girl went missing from her small Oregon town. As police set their sights on one person in particular, a key piece of evidence comes into play, followed by a body. Although you’d think these things would help answer some questions, they do quite the opposite. This is the murder of Leah Freeman.
